                  <div><span class="text-site-muted/50 mr-1.5">[14:32:05]</span><span class="text-electric-cyan font-semibold mr-2">INFO</span><span class="text-site-text/80">kubectl: eu-west-1 (EKS) — API server reachable</span></div>
